title:
Visuals form identity & speak 
for your brand.
body:
# Meet me

First of all I’m a big admirer and collector of everyday object with the beliefe that they can envoke emotions in the viewer’s eyes. 

A still life and product photographer working solo or in the asisstence of my two dogs. My practise focuses on setting direction in your content through sensibility, colors and set design. 

International availablilty gives me opportunity to meet and work with passionate product owners all around the world. You are a product owner? I love to hear your story.
